Also called a "sentinel shield", this targe is emblazoned with a symbol of an eye. While holding this shield, a creature with the [[Mark of Sentinel]] gains +1 [[impact]] when detecting hidden dangers, and -1 [[risk]] when taking their first action when ambushed or surprised by enemies.